name: REFRACT - The GIFs - GIF-r28/48

GIF 28 of 48.

This GIF is part of C5 along with GIF-r25, GIF-r26 and GIF-r27. First 11 collectors to complete C5 will be awarded with 1 edition of OBJKT#XXXXXX (to be revealed on Oct 7th).

First 11 collectors to complete the serie will be awarded with 1 edition of REFRACT -AV- (to be revealed on Oct 8th). 

Items from this collection will be minted and swaped once a day from Aug 20th to Oct 6th.
